    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html>

    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Co-Block | Order Confirmation</title>
    </head>

    <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0">
        <table style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px">
            <tr>
                <td colspan="4" style="text-align: left; background-color: #fff">
                    <span>
                        <img src="./public/images/co-bloc-logo.jpg" alt="co-bloc logo">
                    </span>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="4" style="text-align: center; background-color: #fff">
                    <h1 style="color: #112655; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 600">Order Confirmation</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>

                    <div>
                        <p>Dear <%= Customer_Name %>,</p>
                        <p>Thank you for purchasing Co-bloc game. This email is to inform you that your order has been
                            dispatched
                            and will be delivered in the next 3 to 5 working days to the following address:</p>
                    </div>                
                    
                    <table style="width:100%; border:0;">
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width:70%">
                                
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div>
                        <h6 style="
                            margin: 0;
                            color: #000;
                            font-family: Poppins;
                            font-size: 18px;
                            font-style: normal;
                            font-weight: 600; 
                            margin-bottom: 0 !important;
                            padding-bottom: 8px;
                            ">
                            Billing Address
                        </h6>
                        <h6 style="
                            margin: 0;
                            color: #676363;
                            font-family: Poppins;
                            font-size: 15px;
                            font-style: normal;
                            font-weight: 700;
                            margin-bottom: 0 !important;
                            padding-bottom: 10px;
                            ">
                            <%= Customer_Name %>
                        </h6>
                        <p style="
                            color: #a5aaba;
                            font-family: Poppins;
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-style: normal;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            list-style: none;
                            margin-bottom: 5px;
                            margin-top: 0;
                            ">
                            Street : <%= Billing_Street %>
                        </p>
                        <p style="
                            color: #a5aaba;
                            font-family: Poppins;
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-style: normal;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            list-style: none;
                            margin-bottom: 0 !important;
                            margin: 0;
                            ">
                            City : <%= Billing_City %>
                        </p>
                        <p style="
                            color: #a5aaba;
                            font-family: Poppins;
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-style: normal;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            list-style: none;
                            margin-bottom: 0 !important;
                            margin: 0;
                            ">
                            Country : <%= Billing_Country %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <p>Best regards,</p>
                    <p>Co bloc</p><br>
                    <div class="note">
                        <p><em>Note:</em> This email has been automatically generated. Please do not reply. If you have any
                            questions, please visit our <a href="https://co-bloc.fr/get-in-touch.html">support center</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <table style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; bottom: 20px; position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);">
                        <tr style="padding: 10px 0">
                            <td style="padding: 10px; width: 300px">
                                <p style="text-align:center; padding:10px">
                                    &copy; Entertainment-lab SAS</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
    </body>

    </html>
